  "keyFeatures": [
    "3D Boolean operations (union, intersection, difference) on meshes and voxels",
    "Mesh repair: self-intersection removal, hole filling, degeneracy fixes",
    "Mesh decimation and simplification with configurable tolerance",
    "Mesh offsetting with multiple modes for 3D printing and machining",
    "Point cloud triangulation and normal generation",
    "ICP and multiway registration for mesh/point cloud alignment",
    "Collision detection between 3D models",
    "Voxel-based operations using OpenVDB",
    "Extensive file format support: STL, OBJ, PLY, CTM, DICOM, and more",
    "GPU acceleration via CUDA",
    "Cross-platform: Windows, macOS, Linux, WebAssembly",
    "Multi-language: C++, C, C#, Python bindings"
  ],
